data.description: Back on market at no fault to the sellers. Buyer could no longer obtain financing. Come check out the new floors, new light fixtures, and fresh paint in this 4 bedroom, 2 bath, & 2 car garage property on just over a third of an acre in the beautiful area of Cold Springs. This home features high ceilings that allow for plenty of natural light and a large shed in the backyard for additional storage space. It has also been verified that the pellet stove is in compliance with Washoe County requirements and will save the future owner money on energy expenses to heat the house. The roof is 7 years old and is in great condition. Call today to schedule your showing.
